Start(); if( status == ER_OK ) {
status = msgBus-
Connect(NULL);
}




Implementing a Sink


Implementing a Sink to receive streaming audio requires
creating and registering an instance of the StreamObject class.


NOTE:
 Verify the BusAttachment has been created, started and
