busAttachment, 
msg, 
status);
}




At the conclusion of the processing chain after calling

AJApp_MessageProcessor()
, any unprocessed messages are
processed by the default AllJoyn message processor.


if (serviceStatus == AJSVC_SERVICE_STATUS_NOT_HANDLED) {
   //Pass to the built-in bus message handlers status = AJ_BusHandleBusMessage(
msg);
}




